HEADWORD: launching
<hw>launching</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>the act of moving a
newly-built vessel into the water for the first time.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>the act of beginning something new.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> debut, first appearance, unveiling, introduction,
entry.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>the act of propelling with force.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> launch.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>launchpad</ent>⟦br⟧
